caption:
→ Crowley has something no other demons have, especially not Hastur: an imagination. Right now he’s imagining that he’s just fine, and that a ton of burning metal, rubber and leather is a fully functioning car. He had started the journey in his Bentley, and he was damned if he wasn’t going to finish it in the Bentley as well.

summary: Just finished Good Omens, finally, and I can feel my heart bursting with rainbows. I’ve never been happier for an adaptation in...
body:
Just finished Good Omens, finally, and I can feel my heart bursting with rainbows. I’ve never been happier for an adaptation in my life, I still can’t believe how utterly PERFECT it was.
Thank you Neil, thank you in spirit sir Terry, thank you Michael, thank you David and thank you to everyone who was involved in this masterpiece.

I’m going to cry now, then I’ll start watching it all over again.
